title: 'Worth the price'
body: Honestly at this price this is a steal. The overall quality of the journal is absolutely amazing. It got a clothbound textured hard covering. The paper quality is good and could be used for gouache paintings aswell, the paper might wrinkle a little but it'll be okay once it dries out. You can use it for several purposes. Some gel pens might get imprinted on the other side so i would recommend using a ball point pen, and avoid using sketch pens and markers. It also come with a small compartment at the end of the journal for storing documents aswell. Totally worth the price.
